{"lemma":"إِوَزُّ","slug":"إِوَزُّ","root":"#.ز.ز","root_slug":"_-ز-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ز-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1489"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B2%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singulative of إِوَزّ (ʔiwazz)","tags":["form-of","singulative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1489","headword_ar":"اـِوَزٌّ","root":"Awz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwaz~apN","text_ar":"اـِوَزَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or the latter is the n. un. of the former, [which is a coll. gen. n.,] (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baT~N","text_ar":"بَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"geese;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"duck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ducks;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awz~","text_ar":"اوزّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is generally applied to the former of these birds; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bT~","text_ar":"بطّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to the latter; agreeably with a statement in the Jm, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baT~N","text_ar":"بَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied by the Arabs to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwaz~N","text_ar":"اـِوَزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waz~N","text_ar":"وَزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the n. un. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waz~apN","text_ar":"وَزَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwaz~N","text_ar":"اـِوَزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEal~N","text_ar":"فِعَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) [but see what follows:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwaz~uwna","text_ar":"اـِوَزُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) a form which is sometimes used, (S, Msb,) and which is anomalous. (Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kurokiY~N","text_ar":"كُرْكِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwaz~N","text_ar":"اـِوَزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Short and thick:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleshy without being tall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) El-'Okberee asserts that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is augmentative, because it is followed by three radical letters: (MF, TA:) but ISd says that it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEal~N","text_ar":"فِعَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and may not be of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoEalN","text_ar":"اـِفْعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e., originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iwozazN","text_ar":"اـِوْزَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] because this does not occur as the measure of an epithet. (TA.) [It seems, however, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awz~","text_ar":"اوزّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in this case a subst. used tropically as an epithet, after the manner of many nicknames.] ―         -b3-  Also, applied to a man, and to a horse, and to a camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Firm in make:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHei in the Expos. of the Tes-heel, and TA:) or, applied to a horse,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact and strong in make."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Lth","TA","MF"]}]}}